                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2445" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0176</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8780 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">难舍繁华最深处—北方世纪广告公司做时代勇敢的傻瓜</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Unforgettable the Flourishing Deepest: Northern Century AD Company Acted As a Times’ Brave Fool</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">雷善玉，王静等</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连新北方世纪策划创意有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">地产广告；激励理论；职业精神；合法性；创业Effectuation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Real Estate Advertising; Option Incentive; Professionalism; Legitimacy; Entrepreneurial Effectuation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在当前经济全球化、信息数字化、新媒体不断出现的新时代新环境下，公司特别是初创公司如何抓住环境变化所带来的机遇，学习和掌握一定的应对技巧，适时转变经营模式以适应环境的变化是所有企业面临而又急需探索解决的难题和挑战。本案例描述大连北方世纪广告公司的创始人杨总在地产广告领域创业初期发展迅速却因为疏忽管理致使公司发生财务危机，而在地产业低迷、地产广告的传播范式改变时期，他却以“以正和以奇胜”的战略，集中重建职业精神、内部业务能力升级，重视亲社会化行为和借TVB传播模式而蜕变，在大连地产广告业界中取得了领先地位。本案例适于讨论和学习时代变迁企业究竟应该如何变革治理，创业过程的效果逻辑与因果逻辑，以及从制度学的合法性视角探讨企业的让城市变得更美好的亲社会化利他行为如何能够帮助企业形成自己的核心竞争力问题。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In today’s new era and environment of economic globalization, information digitization and unceasing emerging new media, for firms, especially for those start-ups ones, it’s how to seize opportunities accompanied by environment change, learn and master certain skills to deal with, and timely transform business pattern to stand out that has been becoming a great hard problem and challenge that have to face and explore to settle urgently, This case describes Mr. Yang —founder of Dalian Northern Century AD Company — has developed the company rapidly but he got in financial crisis because of negligence management at the early entrepreneurial stage in real estate advertising business service field, while at the stage of real estate industry murky and spread paradigm change of real estate advertising, he began to build strategy engaging in regular way and trying to win by no regular way to focus on reconstructing professionalism, upgrading internal business capabilities, paying attention to prosocial behavior and depending on TVB (Three dimensional-Viral-Brand) mode to transform the company, so that finally it became the top and only one in local real estate advertising business service industry. This case is good to discuss and learn how firms should transform and govern in accordance with time changed, entrepreneurial logic including effectuation and causation, as well as from the perspective of institutional legitimacy, how the prosocial behavior of firms - to make the city more better - as altruistic behaviors to help enterprises to form their own core competitiveness.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2015</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》、《创新与创业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">变革</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2016-09</td>
